{
  "name": "WF-07-AGENT-EXECUTOR-V15",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## WF-07 — Agent Executor V15\n**Exército Comercial de IA — Motor Principal**\n\nV15: LangSmith tracing + real token/cost tracking.\n- Code - Capture Start: captura _start_time antes do AI Agent\n- Code - Calc Metrics: calcula tokens, custo, duração e gera langsmith_run_id\n- HTTP - Insert Run: agora preenche tokens_input, tokens_output, cost_usd, duration_ms, langsmith_run_id\n- HTTP - Send LangSmith: envia run para api.smith.langchain.com\n\n**TESTE MANUAL (após importar):**\nPOST https://n8n.julianosalles.com.br/webhook-test/agent-executor\n```json\n{\n  \"conversation_id\": \"483ff60f-909d-471e-ab53-109f916ad389\",\n  \"lead_id\": \"bcd4c7d6-a349-4e6b-8b48-0fd7023802fb\",\n  \"agent_id\": \"809664ac-d7cb-4280-a573-f251cca9d100\",\n  \"company_id\": \"32a1ab33-e2f2-4c33-b6b4-5a4d00e7e2ed\",\n  \"input_text\": \"Olá, tenho interesse no produto\",\n  \"content_type\": \"text\"\n}\n```",
        "height": 360,
        "width": 560,
        "color": 4
      },
